txt.en: Gundabad pack-leaders and Gundabad pack-hunters can be found in the Floodfells.\n\nYou should defeat the Gundabad pack-leaders and Gundabad pack-hunters.
Sighild, daughter of Runerik and Yrsa, seeks to put an end to the packs of Wargs still roaming the Floodfells.

'Wargs, I hate them. Skarding hates them more, but I hate them almost as much! They have no regard for the creatures of the wilds. They kill animals for amusement! It sickens me. Their packs roam the lands between Khilbakh and Ylgraf. We must reclaim these lands from the Wargs. They have no right to the Floodfells.'
